These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, oliveros, prince, vegafina
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, water-polo, basketball
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, scrabble, chess
House: craftsman, wooden, ranch-style, cottage
There 4 different types of food: banana, cabbage, apricot, blueberry
 1. the person eating banana is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 2. the person playing chess is between the swisher-smoker and the person eating blueberry##2
 3. the craftsman house is the person eating blueberry##1
 4. the wooden house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 5. the person eating banana is between the swisher-smoker and the person playing scrabble##2
 6. the cottage house is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 7. the person eating cabbage is the prince-smoker##1
 8. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Cigar           | prince | swisher   | vegafina | oliveros |
| Sport   | rowing      | rugby | water-polo              | basketball |
| Game   | mah-jongg       | backgammon     | chess               | scrabble    |
| House           | wooden        | ranch-style     | cottage           | craftsman       |
| Food     | cabbage | apricot     | banana                | blueberry      |

