.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, siglo, oliveros, prince
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, coral, blue, yellow
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, train, snowmobile, jet-ski
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, poppy, zinnia, azalea
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, thai, japanese, australian
 1. the person who likes blue is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 3. the person who likes coral is between the oliveros-smoker and the person who growspoppy##2
 4. the person driving the jet-ski is the brazilian##1
 5. the person who growszinnia is the person who likes coral##1
 6. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 7. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 8. the thai is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 9. the japanese is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
10. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
11. the brazilian is the oliveros-smoker##1
12. the davidoff-smoker is the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Cigar          | oliveros       | siglo      | davidoff      | prince      |
| Color           | yellow | coral | blue | brown |
| Transport   | jet-ski          | train       | snowmobile            | subway      |
| Flower           | sunflower            | zinnia    | poppy           | azalea       |
| Nationality         | brazilian        | thai    | japanese         | australian  |

