 7. the journalist is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 8. the person who growslily is the french##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the dutch and the owner of the turtle##2
10. the victorian house is on the far left##1
11. the cottage house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Flower      | daisy     | balloon-flower | begonia    | lily          |
| House          | victorian | wooden     | art-deco | cottage         |
| Pet   | turtle    | frog       | ferret         | mouse        |
