 4. the person playing bridge is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 6. the owner of the horse is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 7. the person playing snooker is the person who growsazalea##1
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 9. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
10. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person playing snooker##2
12. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person playing bridge and the person who growsamaryllis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Flower      | zinnia      | amaryllis         | azalea | marigold      |
| Birthday           | february | july | september | october     |
| Pet   | cat         | horse          | guinea-pig  | dog |
| Hobby         | skydiving        | drawing  | baking | magic-tricks   |
| Game     | chess    | whist         | snooker     | bridge     |

