.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-19::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, canasta, pineapple
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, lime, blueberry, cranberry
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, november, june
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, scientific, animation, musical
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, turkish, canadian, british
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is the person eating lime##1
 2. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person watching musical movies and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is the person watching superhero movies##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing mah-jongg and the british##2
 6. the turkish is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 7. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating pineapple is the canadian##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1

