.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, december, august, september
4 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, poker, scrabble
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, dunhill, bluemaster, old-henry
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, eggplant, grapes, spinach
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, iris, lily, sunflower
 1. the person playing scrabble is the dunhill-smoker##1
 2. the person who growssunflower is between the old-henry-smoker and the person eating artichoke##2
 3. the person who growsiris is between the person eating eggplant and the person who growslily##2
 4. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the person playing poker is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
 6. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the person playing poker is the person eating grapes##1
 9. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growslily##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is the bongani-smoker##1
11. the bongani-smoker is the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Birthday         | august  | december | september | january |
| Game   | scrabble      | monopoly   | poker      | billiard    |
| Cigar   | dunhill  | bluemaster | old-henry        | bongani     |
| Food         | artichoke  | eggplant  | grapes     | spinach      |
| Flower     | aconite | sunflower      | iris   | lily       |

 